From: Nick Piggin <npiggin@suse.de>
Subject: [patch 8/9] mm: spinlock tree_lock

mapping->tree_lock has no read lockers. convert the lock from an rwlock
to a spinlock.

Signed-off-by: Nick Piggin <npiggin@suse.de>

